title: Episode 13 - Sienna Mae Gomez
description:
Sienna Mae Gomez comes on for the least toxic interview the guys have ever done. Josh responds to Jackson Mahomes trying to steal his girl. We introduce our newest game '04 or Before? Brianna explains the craze behind "Drivers License" and the guys listen to Lil Huddy's new banger.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
